title: 08/19/2021 DPS Hour 2 Zach Wilson and Justin Fields Expectations
itunes:title: 08/19/2021 DPS Hour 2 Zach Wilson and Justin Fields Expectations
description:
Jonas Knox, Brady Quinn and LaVar Arrington, in for Dan, debate which rookie QB will have the best season and LaVar takes a hard stance on Zach Wilson. In Chicago, Andy Dalton says "it's his time," but the guys know it's a short matter of time before it's turned over to Justin Fields. Plus, a preview of the Patriots at the Eagles on Over/Under.
